clusterList.phrase: helen and betty could not be more different in their perspectives of the destitute people that live around them when helen the old sister hears the story of the good samaritan she is rewarded for her classroom achievements while the other sister chooses to live the example of the good samaritan as helen lives for herself and is constantly worried about the opinions of others betty searches for ways to be a blessing to others when faced with the realities of living the life of the good samaritan helen reveals the treachery of her own heart as she mercilessly withholds good from a dirty street urchin this is a story that reaches the heart especially when you read how helen responds to unexpected mercy and forgiveness she did not deserve
